WEBVTT

00:00.995 --> 00:02.710
Previously on The Originals...

00:02.713 --> 00:04.606
I guess I'll see you in the next life.

00:04.609 --> 00:07.320
I'll be waiting for another dance.

00:07.323 --> 00:10.242
My mother... you let her die.

00:13.637 --> 00:16.104
Hope's taking the power from us.

00:23.312 --> 00:25.804
If he dies, I won't just lose him...

00:26.846 --> 00:29.039
...I'll trigger my curse.

00:29.042 --> 00:31.142
The dark magic is destroying Hope

00:31.145 --> 00:32.377
from the inside out.

00:32.378 --> 00:33.822
So how do we stop it?

00:33.825 --> 00:35.379
There's nothing we can do.

00:35.382 --> 00:38.054
She's my daughter.

